# Additional
Growth Tracking: Visual indicators showing percentage growth/decline for sales and volume.
Technical Features
Data Modeling: Integrated sales data across multiple dimensions including Body Style, Transmission, and Engine types.
Advanced Visualizations:
Area Chart: Weekly sales trends over time.
Map Integration: Geographic distribution of sales across different regions.
Donut & Bar Charts: Breakdown of sales by car type and manufacturer.
Interactivity: Built-in Slicers for Body Style, Transmission, and Engine to allow for deep-dive filtering.
Dynamic Navigation: Custom sidebar menu for easy switching between Overview and Details views.
